# Testing Standards

Follow the canonical standard: **`.ai/standards/testing.md`**

Key rules:
- Respect the pyramid: unit, integration, system/E2E
- Test files mirror the structure of the code under test
- API endpoints cover happy path + auth failure + validation errors
- No skipped/pending tests without a ticket reference

